Fix: a runaway explode no longer runs forever and wedges the whole app.

Root cause: a DuckDB read is materialized with one COPY (...) TO parquet, which
holds the engine's connection lock for its whole duration. An UNNEST cross-
product on the nested "json" column (e.g. receivingLeg x payingLeg) can produce
