seconds instead of pinning the engine. The fallback drain path stops at the same
ceiling. When a result is capped, a notification toast says so ("Result capped
-- stopped at the N-row safety limit; add a filter or raise
SAMQL_MAX_RESULT_ROWS") -- one toast on the run, no inline clutter.

