An API node (including each pass of an iterator or while loop) that fetched an
endpoint returning something other than JSON -- an HTML login or error page,
plain text, or an empty body -- used to fail with a raw "JSONDecodeError:
Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0)", which says nothing about what
