fetch, only the message shown when a response can't be read as JSON. The
variable substitution and the loop itself were never the problem -- the error
already showed the date resolving correctly.

Reasoned vs tested: covered by a new test that drives the loader's streaming
path with an injected spooler returning an HTML page and an empty body, and
